content.script:
::Aries:: I hope I will see you again.
::Aries:: Take care!
<FadeOut()>

<FadeIn()>
::Kenji::Hello.
::Scorpio:: We need to talk. [serious]
::Scorpio::I need someone that can help me with something.
::Kenji::Ok....
::Scorpio::I know you don't know too much about weapons, but maybe you will be useful with something else.
::Scorpio::I need to craft one of the rarest swords that was ever seen on this town.
::Kenji:: How do you know I can't craft weapons?
::Scorpio::I can just tell that.
::Scorpio::The weapon is for me by the way, not a custom offer.
::Kenji:: How can I help you?
::Scorpio::The sword is not driven by any stone.
::Scorpio::It takes power from its owner more than anything.
::Kenji::Do you want me to give my life for this sword?
::Scorpio::No, no. Nothing extreme like that.
::Scorpio::The sword feeds on its owner emotions, not life.
::Kenji::I am still not sure how I can help you.
::Scorpio::Can you hang out with me?
::Kenji::Excuse me?
::Scorpio::You heard me right. Can you just hang out with me?
::Kenji::I am sure this is  a prank, but I am not sure how to feel about it.
::Scorpio::Look, I don't have friends.
::Scorpio::The closest person to me is Valerie, but for this sword, I need a male.
::Narrator:: Valerie was a common friend of ours, another Goddess.


::Scorpio::And here is where you come in.
::Kenji::Why me and not someone else?
::Scorpio::Because you are the closest to me.
::Scorpio::Well, literally.
::Scorpio::Also, if you don't do well, I can't fire and then kill you.
::Scorpio::Or the other way around.  I will have to decide later.
::Kenji::I am not sure the last one makes any sense.
::Scorpio::Do you really want to tell a goddess of war, what makes sense and what not?
::Kenji::I have no idea what foolish soul said anything in here.
::Kenji::I will find him and make sure he pays with his own life.
::Scorpio::You should do just that.
::Kenji::So, let me see if I understood this right.
::Kenji::If I help you, this sword might make you really strong.
::Scorpio::That's correct.
::Kenji::But if I refuse, I am going to get killed.
::Scorpio::That's also correct.
::Kenji::Do I have a third option or nah?
::Scorpio::Absolutely not.
::Kenji::Well, I have a feeling out of nowhere to hang out with you.
::Kenji::Please tell me more about you and what your dreams are.
::Scorpio::See. It wasn't that tough.
::Kenji::You are not the one that will die if they refuse.
::Kenji::But seriously now, do we just need to talk?
::Kenji::How does this sword work?
::Scorpio::I am not quite sure myself.
::Scorpio::I already have it but it did nothing for me so far.
::Scorpio::I thought maybe I was not strong enough but then I realized.
::Scorpio::What if I was looking at it the wrong way all this time?
::Scorpio::What if it was another emotion? 
::Kenji::What could it be?
::Scorpio::Love.
::Kenji::Eh? Are you serious?
::Scorpio::A lot of mystical weapons have been hidden from people.
::Scorpio::Most of them have a love story behind them.
::Scorpio::Think about it.
::Scorpio::People started wars because of love, people killed others because of love and people betrayed because of love.
::Kenji::I don't think that's quite right.
::Kenji::People did all those things because of jealousy, not love.
::Scorpio::I found them to be strongly connected with each other.
::Kenji::That might be true, but even then, do you need to experience love or jealousy?
::Scorpio::Again, I will probably experience both but I think love is the key.
::Scorpio::Don't look at me like that. I realize how stupid I sound.
::Scorpio::I tried everything else though and I need this sword.
::Kenji::Fine, fine. I will help you.
::Kenji::What should we do now?
::Scorpio::No idea. I was never in love as you can tell and never cared about other guys.
::Scorpio::I just wanted to fight my whole life. For an eternity I was only interested about wars and fights.
::Kenji::We should probably start with knowing more about each other.
::Kenji::What do you like to do?
::Scorpio::Start wars and kill others for their stupidity.
::Kenji::Maybe something more romantic than that?
::Kenji::Walks on the beach?
::Scorpio::Only if we need to fight there.
::Kenji::Just spending time with someone really close? Maybe hugging them?
::Scorpio::The only people that I hug are the death ones when I needed to hide from deadly arrows.
::Kenji::Aha.
::Kenji::Maybe your favorite drink or food.
::Kenji::Please don't even answer that. I assume it will be the blood and tears of your enemies.
::Scorpio::Heyyy! I think we are getting to know each other more than we thought.
::Kenji::Yes. I am not worried about it at all.
::Scorpio::Is this working already? Let me check.
::Scorpio::Unfortunately the sword is not responding.
::Kenji::What should even happen?
::Scorpio::The color should change and I will feel a lot of power going through me.
::Kenji::That is something I would love to see.
::Kenji::If that's all you needed help with, can I go now?
::Scorpio::I suppose so, but we need to meet again too.
::Scorpio::This clearly wasn't enough for the sword.

scripts.name: 2 - Script

content.script:
::Kenji::Hello, Scorpio! I see you are in high spirits today.
::Scorpio::I have talked with other people and I have a list of what things we can do to help the sword.
::Kenji::Aha. What will that include?
::Scorpio::Most of them are ridiculous, but I will tell you.
::Scorpio::Going on a picnic date, spending time with each other on the beach.
::Kenji::Those seem pretty normal to me.
::Scorpio::Wait. Listen here.
::Scorpio::Try to get closer to each other and hug. That's just stupid.
::Kenji::Of course. Who would want to do something like that? Seems like a waste of time.
::Scorpio::I am glad you understand it.
::Scorpio::Share a meal together that one of you prepared.
::Kenji::Who are these people?
::Scorpio::That's what I am wondering too. I should get new friends for sure.
::Scorpio::These things are just a waste of time. Even you agree with m...
::Scorpio::Wait a second.
::Scorpio::Are you making fun of me?
::Kenji::If the honest answer will spare my life, then yes.
::Kenji::If that answer will kill me, then I have no idea what you are talking about and those people are clear idiots.
::Scorpio::You don't need to worry about your life.
::Scorpio::I was just joking when we met.
::Kenji::Yes... hahaha.
::Kenji::I am still laughing thinking about my head rolling on the ground without my body.
::Kenji::That's just hilarious.
::Scorpio::Do you want to try all these things with me?
::Scorpio::I know I am a burden to you. I really don't know any other way to act honestly. [sad]
::Scorpio::I heard about people getting married, of course I did.
::Scorpio::But it was mostly for the title or to have kids that can fight other battles.
::Scorpio::For a long time now, there hasn't been a real war.
::Scorpio::I feel like I have almost no purpose here.
::Scorpio::And looking at the others, I wonder if I wasted all this time.
::Scorpio::Sure, an eternity sounds nice, but think about it.
::Scorpio::You get to see so many things that you will rather forget and does anything have any meaning if all of this is eternal?
::Kenji::Well, those are some big questions to ask.
::Kenji::I don't know honestly.
::Kenji::I thought every God will do what they are the best at without thinking about it.
::Scorpio::I will let you know a secret.
::Scorpio::Gods are not defined by the thing they do. They don't have to follow that because it is how the stones have said.
::Scorpio::Gods are getting a title because they were really good at that.
::Scorpio::You probably knew that already, but you knew that some of us don't like that anymore?
::Scorpio::I have found myself wondering what's the point of fighting sometimes.
::Scorpio::I used to love it so much in the past, but now....
::Scorpio::I am not sure what to tell you.
::Scorpio::Trying to keep my act for the others around me can be tiring.
::Scorpio::I got to see so many families left without their sons and I never got to experience love or other things like humans did.
::Scorpio::Gods experience that too, but I was always busy with wars. I hope it doesn't sound too stupid.
::Kenji::No. I get what you mean.
::Kenji::You are trapped by the destiny you brought upon yourself?
::Scorpio::You could say it like that.
::Scorpio::I never imagined I would get to this point.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.2 - Script

scripts.name: 1 - Start

content.script:
<ChageLocation(Kenji_House_Outside)>
<FadeIn()>
::Narrator:: I just exit from my house when I saw a familiar face standing there. 
::Narrator:: I was hoping to see anyone else, except her.
::Narrator:: I would love to try and ignore her presence, but that will probably mean my death.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.1 - Start

content.script:
::Aries::Sure. You are free to come here whenever you feel like it.
::Aries::Just please be careful if you come at night.
::Kenji::Thank you!
::Aries::You will find me in the same spot. I usually spend my time here.
::Kenji::I will remember that.
::Aries::Have a good night and hope we will see each other again.
::Kenji::See you around!
<FadeOut()>
// Created on : Wed Apr 07 2021 10:42:50 GMT-0300 (Argentina Standard Time)

::Aries::I feel the same way about you too.
::Aries::I didn't meet too many people in my life.
::Aries::Well, never one that was so close to me at least.
::Aries::Most of them just wanted to use me for my powers or were just mean with the animals.
::Aries::You accepted me how I am and I wanted to thank you for that.

::Narrator:: We both hugged and stood like that for what felt like an eternity. 
::Narrator:: It was like none of us wanted this moment to end and we were lost in our own universe that we created with one embrace.

scripts.name: Kenji finds Aries

content.script:
::Kenji::Hi! Is it really you?
::Aries::Eh?
::Aries::Sorry, but you scared me to death.
::Aries::I wanted to visit the temple and talk with the priestess here and after I was going to visit you.
::Kenji::I am really happy you decided to come. 
::Kenji::I can wait for you if you have unfinished businesses.
::Aries::It's ok. I don't seem to find her anyway.
::Kenji::Are you sure?
::Aries::Of course. Please don't worry about me.
::Aries::I honestly came here to see you more than anything.
::Kenji::You are very sweet. I can show you around if you want.
::Aries::I would love to. 
::Aries::I rarely come here so it will be nice to grasp this place better.
::Kenji::Follow me!

::Narrator:: I showed Aries around the town.
::Narrator:: We looked at the market, palace and anything else that I thought will be interesting to her.
::Narrator:: She mostly nodded and looked surprised whenever I told her anything about the history of this place.

::Aries::Can we rest a little? I never visited so many places in my life.
::Kenji::Really?
::Aries::You know where I live already. Not too much to see there.
::Kenji::But you can always come here and see the town.
::Aries::I don't want to let anyone down back home.
::Aries::I really like this place too though.
::Aries::I am grateful and overjoyed that you showed me around.
::Aries::I should go back home soon though. I never was out as much as now.
::Aries:: Don't want anyone to worry about me.
::Aries::Plus, what if something happened home?
::Kenji::You can feel it, right?
::Aries::What?
::Kenji::You can feel if something is going bad there, right?
::Aries::Well, kind of.
::Kenji::Can you please stay for a couple of minutes at least ?
::Aries::Sure, I can do that.
::Kenji::I want to know more about you.
::Aries::There's not much more to say.
::Aries::As you know, I love animals and I can live forever.
::Kenji::Do you have a favorite animal?
::Aries::Hmmm. I never thought about it.
::Aries::I try to love them all equally.
::Kenji::Like a parent will do.
::Aries::Exactly.
::Aries::Other than that, I want to have a party in the forest.
::Kenji::A party?
::Aries::I saw other people doing it. They call it camping.
::Kenji::You never tried that before?
::Kenji::Although it might be weird for you to camp in your own house.
::Aries::I just didn't have anyone to do it with.
::Aries::What do you think about it?
::Kenji::That actually sounds like fun.
::Kenji::When do you want us to do it?
::Aries::Are you serious?
::Aries::You will actually do this for me?
::Kenji::Not for you, but with you.
::Kenji::I want to try this too. Honestly, I never went camping either.
::Kenji::My parents weren't that much into nature.
::Aries::That's nice.
::Aries::I mean the part where you want to do it with me, not disliking the nature.
::Aries::I feel like I should really go now though.
::Aries::Next time, we might be able to go camping if you want it.
::Aries::Should I look for a place?
::Kenji::I think it is better if we just search it together.
::Kenji::I am sure you know the whole forest, but it should be more fun this way.
::Aries::Ok. I would love that too.

::Narrator:: Aries wanted to leave. I was not sure what to do thinking that I want to tell her how I feel about all this.

scripts.path: Dialogues.03 - Aries visits Kenji.Kenji finds Aries

content.script:
::Aries:: I am happy I could do something good for both of you.
::Aries:: Tell the owner to be more careful with their pet.
::Kenji:: I will.

::Narrator:: I can't believe she actually helped me and ask nothing in return. Well, I should not think too much about it. 
::Narrator:: It is late and I st ill have to return the little fella to his owner.

<FadeOut()>

scripts.name: Kenji meet Aries in the forest

content.script:
::Aries:: [waving] Hello there!
::Aries:: I see you came again as promised.
::Kenji:: Of course. I see you are in the middle of something. Quite literally.
::Aries:: [laughing] Haha, yes. It is ok guys, he is with me.

::Narrator:: Just then, a couple of cute looking hedgehogs moved from the circle to create a path for me. 
::Narrator:: I could have probably jumped over them with ease, but it was kind of cute to see them moving and stumbling into each other.

::Kenji:: Sorry guys! I am new here.
::Aries:: Hahaha. Don't worry about it.
::Aries:: They will love you. As long as you are with me.
::Kenji:: Aha. Do you sing for yourself or for them too?
::Aries:: It depends on how I feel. We have meetings sometimes but now we are just hanging around like this.
::Aries:: We formed a circle because that's the best way to see everyone. Well, at least for them.
::Aries:: I can't see behind me, but I can feel the animal's presence.
::Kenji:: I see. I hope I didn't interrupt them.
::Kenji:: I would not like to piss some dangerous animals off and get stabbed in the back by a hedgehog.
::Aries:: That will be quite the sight.
::Aries:: We are peaceful around here though.
::Aries:: At night other animals come , but now everyone is just relaxing.
::Kenji:: This is really nice. What do you usually discuss at meetings?
::Aries:: I listen to every breed and we try to decide what's best for everyone.
::Kenji:: So it is like a community. Well, a more sophisticated one than I expected.
::Aries:: Yes. By talking with them, I can have eyes over the whole forest.
::Aries:: It will be impossible to know what's happening otherwise.
::Kenji:: I can't believe I never knew about it.
::Aries:: No one really knows about this. I showed it to you because I was moved you cared about the little pet.
::Kenji:: But it wasn't anything special.
::Aries:: Maybe not for you. I know there's other people that care about animals, but you were the first that actually came to the forest to look for one.
::Aries:: Others mostly came here for fun and dangerous games.
::Kenji:: Do they get killed? My parents told me a lot of horrifying stories about this place at night.
::Aries:: I am not going to tell you.
::Aries:: Just don't step in the empty holes we dug. Those are clearly for something else.
::Kenji:: [scared] What???
::Aries:: [laughing] I am just teasing you. I don't know if anybody died here.
::Aries:: Protecting these animals and place is already hard enough. This is basically my home.
::Aries:: I try to protect people too, but I can't interfere if they choose to fight animals. Only to protect ourselves if the fight is not fair.
::Aries:: You might think this is crude, but I need to let others have free will too. 
::Aries:: I will step only if something is unfair.
::Kenji:: Who determines what is unfair?
::Aries:: Well, between animals almost everything it's fair.
::Aries:: It's just when humans hunt them. I understand the occasional hunt and that sometimes the population is too high.
::Aries:: Do I think there's other solutions? Probably.
::Aries:: But I need to keep a balance between everything. But if some people come here just to hurt animals and they have weapons or choose to destroy parts of the forest...
::Aries:: I can't let that go unpunished.
::Aries:: It is difficult for me to talk about what's right or wrong still...
::Aries:: There are times when I know I just have to watch, but my heart tells me to interfere.
::Kenji:: This must be really tough on you.
::Aries:: Well, it is nice most of the time.
::Aries:: And someone needs to look out for this place.
::Kenji:: I understand that. 
::Kenji:: I can see the others want to talk with you, so I will take my leave.
::Kenji:: Thank you for letting me in your council.
::Aries:: Always.
::Aries:: Are you sure you don't want to stay more?
::Kenji:: I have to do some things in the town too.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji visits Aries..Kenji meet Aries in the forest

content.script:
::Aries::I wish I can protect all of them but sometimes they do get lost.
::Kenji::It happens I guess...
::Kenji::Maybe it will be better for him out there.
::Aries::I can see your point, but wild animals are wild.
::Aries::This one is domestic so I think it is better for him to stay with its owner.
::Kenji::I wasn't expecting an answer like that from you.
::Aries:: I said I want to protect them. I think living with a good owner is the best solution for them.
::Aries::They are not used living in the wild and might die from the other animals.
::Aries::I try to not intervene in that. It's the way nature goes.
::Kenji::Aren't you the nature?
::Aries::I am the one that tries to protects it, that's all.
::Aries::I can talk with the animals and help them with some things, but not mess with the natural flow.
::Kenji::I understand. That's an interesting way to look at it.
::Kenji::I am happy we talked.
::Aries::Are you going home now?
::Kenji::Yes. It is pretty late and I kind of lost my hope that I will find him.
::Kenji::Maybe I will come tomorrow once more, but it is probably hopeless.
::Aries::I don't know if I should do this, but please wait here. [worried]
::Kenji::Ok....

::Narrator:: The goddess ran away and left me in the middle of the forest.
::Narrator:: I decided to wait a bit for her, but I was worried that some evil creatures are going to attack me if I stay more.
::Narrator:: I was ready to leave when I saw the goddess returning and running as fast as she could. I think she has something in her hands, but I can't see it quite clear.

::Aries:: So  rrr    yy
::Aries:: F o r    maa   kking
::Kenji:: Please calm down a little. I can wait.
::Aries:: Thank you!
::Aries:: [smiling] Is this the little fella you were looking for?

::Narrator:: She opened her arms and the pet that created me so much trouble appeared.

::Kenji:: I can't believe it. How did you manage to find it?
::Aries:: Well, I really don't know if I should tell you.
::Aries:: No one else is supposed to know this.
::Kenji:: Well, I am just glad you managed to find him
::Kenji:: At first I was just looking for him because I felt bad for the owner, but as I was searching, I started to worry for the pet too.
::Kenji:: I imagine life here is not too easy on someone as small as him.
::Aries:: I am happy I found him. Sometimes it is not that easy.
::Kenji:: You have done this before?
::Aries:: Animals sometimes go astray. Well, mostly the domestic ones.
::Kenji:: Anyway, thank you very much!
::Kenji:: I would have never found him without your help.

::Narrator:: I had to go and visit a place where Scoripo was. We both knew each other for some time, but I can't call her a friend.
::Narrator:: She is the most skilled when it comes to creating weapons and gave me a job at her place but...
::Narrator:: I can't say I am really happy with it since she is a little bit too much at times.
::Narrator:: Upon my arrival, she just came to me and started talking.

scripts.name: 9 - Script

content.script:
::Scorpio:: [smiling] Thank you!
::Scorpio:: [sad] It's very nice of you to say that, but please excuse me.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.9 - Script

scripts.name: 8 - Script

content.script: ::Scorpio:: [sad] I just don't know what to do about it and what my true feelings are.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.8 - Script

content.script:
<ChangeLocation(Forest_01)>

::Narrator:: I decided to visit Aries again in the forest. 
::Narrator:: I felt like I didn't thank her enough and I am also quite interested in her. 
::Narrator:: I never got so close to someone that can talk with animals, I only heard about goddesses like her.
::Narrator:: I entered the forest and I tried to remember the last place where I saw her. 
::Narrator:: Soon enough, I could hear that angelic voice again and I followed it. 
::Narrator:: Only this time, she was not alone. The goddess was in the middle of a circle made by some small animals.
// Created on : Wed Apr 07 2021 18:51:03 GMT-0300 (Argentina Standard Time)

::Narrator:: I was walking around town, close to the Temple, when I saw someone I never thought I will see again or at least not around here.
::Narrator:: Outside the temple it was Aries just standing there.

scripts.name: 5 - End

content.script:
::Scorpio::Thank you! I really don't know what to say.
::Kenji::You don't have to say anything.
::Scorpio::I see. 
::Scorpio::Well,I will do my best to be more of my true self.
::Scorpio::Thank you!

::Narrator:: Scorpio turned around and waved goodbye at me. It wasn't the warmest goodbye, but it was the warmest bye I ever got from her.

scripts.path: Dialogues.03 - Kenji Look for Scorpio.5 - End

content.script:
::Aries::I don't know what to say...
::Aries::I promise you that I will try to find you when I come again there.
::Aries::But please don't worry too much since I rarely came to the town.
::Kenji::It is ok. Whenever you have time and feel like it.
<FadeOut()>

::Narrator:: I can't believe I agreed to help someone find their pet. 
::Narrator:: This morning I saw a paper about someone that lost their animal and I decided to look for it. 
::Narrator:: Sure,the money it's a plus, but I also just wanted to help.

<ScreenMessage(After some time)>

::Narrator:: I searched everywhere in this town, so the last place was the forest
::Narrator:: This part of the town is usually calm, but it can be dangerous if you come here at night.
::Narrator:: A lot of mystical creatures are almost harmless, but that doesn't mean all of them are. 
::Narrator:: Harpies for example can still kill you if they think they are in danger.
::Narrator:: So, even if the sun is still up, I will try to be careful around these places.
::Narrator:: I only came here a couple of years ago with a friend. We used to play here, but only during the mornings.
::Narrator:: I don't know how am I supposed to find that little animal in here. 
::Narrator:: It is half dog and half rabbit but with so many other creatures, this is a nightmare.
::Narrator:: After 6 hours of walking, I wanted to give up. Just then, I heard a beautiful voice coming from the depths of the forest.
::Narrator:: I decided to investigate the sound and see what all of this was about.
::Narrator:: It didn't take much time until I found the source of this. 
::Narrator:: A gorgeous girl was sitting there without any worries in the world. I approached her slowly, trying to not scare her.

::Scorpio::I hope I will see you around.
::Scorpio::Don't move towns because I will find you anyway.
::Kenji::Will do.

::Aries:: I see....
::Aries:: Well, I hope you will see like me in the future.

<FadeOut()>

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.10 - Choice

scripts.name: 2 - Script

content.script:
::Kenji::Hello stranger!
::Scorpio::Hi! How did you manage to find me?
::Kenji::Do you think it's tough to not spot someone that carries a big sword with them?
::Scorpio::You know what I mean.
::Scorpio::How did you know I will be here?
::Kenji::I thought of the most unlikely place you will be in.
::Kenji::Plus, history has all the answers, right?
::Kenji::So it made sense for you to come here.
::Scorpio::You make for a really good general.
::Kenji::Thank you!
::Scorpio::I know I need to go back to my shop, but I just want to stay here a little more.
::Kenji::There's no rush so don't worry.
::Kenji::I can wait here with you.
::Scorpio::Are you sure you want to stay with me?
::Scorpio::I might get annoyed and kill you.
::Kenji::I think it is worth the risk.
::Scorpio::You are crazy.
::Kenji::Said the goddess with a huge sword that is activated by love.
::Scorpio::Honestly, I don't even know if this thing works.
::Scorpio::It could be all just a stupid piece of metal.
::Kenji::Well, we can try more I guess.
::Scorpio::I am not going to put you through anything that you don't want.
::Scorpio::You already saw me in a horrible situation.
::Scorpio::I just wish we can forget about it and move on.
::Kenji::What are you talking about?
::Scorpio::I am talking about me crying.
::Scorpio::I never let anyone see me like this before.
::Kenji::So it did happen before too.
::Scorpio::I look like this, but I am not made of stone.
::Scorpio::I will be back to my usual self in a couple of hours. Just need that time.
::Kenji::To your usual fake self?
::Scorpio::Maybe....
::Scorpio:: [sad] I don't really know what I am anymore. I want to believe in everything I did in the past, but I am not so sure about it anymore.
::Kenji::I don't think anyone will be against you if you change.
::Scorpio::That's not true. Other Gods will laugh at me and humans will start to question my powers.
::Kenji::I was talking about anyone that matters. The people that are close to you.
::Scorpio::Who even is that? I have no one.
::Kenji::Don't say that. You clearly have some people that care about it.
::Kenji::As for me, I do care too and I am here for you.
::Scorpio::You really don't need to pretend anymore. I know you are afraid of me.
::Kenji::I am not.
::Scorpio:: [smiling] Is that how bad I fell? Not even a human is scared of me?
::Kenji:: [sarcastic] Oh noooo! I am terrified. Please don't kill me.
::Kenji::I am begging on my knees for my life.
::Scorpio::That was a great performance.
::Scorpio::Seriously now, you don't need to do this anymore.
::Scorpio::I promise I will not hurt you or say anything about this.
::Kenji::I know that already. I trust that you will not attack me anyway.
::Kenji::I am not doing this because I am scared of you.
::Kenji::At first I was terrified, but I realized we are not that different.
::Kenji::So, I want to be there for you.

scripts.path: Dialogues.03 - Kenji Look for Scorpio.2 - Script

content.script:
::Aries:: Ive been meaning to visit the library for a while now.
::Kenji:: The library? Whats so interesting about a place full of books?
::Aries:: Its not just the books. Its the quiet and the knowledge. You never know what you might find there.
::Kenji:: I guess so. I never really thought about it like that.
::Aries:: Its a place where ideas come to life. Plus, I could use some peace and quiet today.
::Kenji:: I get that. Sometimes its nice to just get away from everything.
::Aries:: Exactly. The library has a calming effect on me. Its like a little escape from the chaos.
::Kenji:: Well, I suppose I could join you. Itll be an interesting experience for me too.
::Aries:: Are you sure? You dont seem like the library type.
::Kenji:: Im open to new experiences. Besides, I could use a change of scenery.
::Aries:: Alright, then. Lets go. Its not far from here.
::Kenji:: Lead the way.

// The characters are entering the library, the environment should feel peaceful and calming.
::Narrator:: The library loomed ahead, quiet and inviting, the doors wide open as if welcoming them in.
::Narrator:: As they stepped inside, the peaceful atmosphere immediately enveloped them, offering a brief respite from the busy world outside.
::Narrator:: The air smelled of old books, and the soft rustling of pages filled the silence, making it a perfect place for reflection.

<PlayBackgroundMusic("calm_library")>  // Play calming background music as they enter the library

::Kenji:: Wow, its... surprisingly peaceful in here.
::Aries:: I told you. Its like the world slows down.
::Kenji:: I can see why you like it. Its a bit... calming.
::Aries:: Thats the idea. Want to find a book to read?
::Kenji:: Sure, Im curious what kind of books you like.
::Aries:: Mostly ones about nature, but sometimes a good mystery is fun.
::Kenji:: Mystery, huh? I think Id like that too.
::Aries:: Theres a whole section over there. Come on, Ill show you.
::Kenji:: Lead the way.

// Add pause to allow the characters to take in the library before continuing
<Pause(2)> 

::Narrator:: As they walked through the library, Aries showed Kenji her favorite books and the little hidden corners where she liked to read.
::Narrator:: It was a peaceful moment, one that made them feel closer as they shared something new together.

<ShowCharacter("Aries", "smiling")>  // Show Aries smiling as she shares the library with Kenji

scripts.name: 1 - Start

content.script:
<ChangeLocation(Library)>
::Narrator:: I was almost sure I will find Scorpio in the place that no one will expect her to be and that's the library. 
::Narrator:: I entered and surely enough, she was there at a table.

content.script:
::Narrator:: Just then, Scorpio ran away and I could see she had tears in her eyes.
::Narrator:: I never thought I will see someone like her cry. It makes me wonder if she even cried before in her life.

scripts.path: Dialogues.02 - Kenji Meet Scorpio Again.7 - End

content.script:
::Girl::Hi there!
::Kenji::Hello! I am sorry.
::Kenji::I didn't mean to interrupt your singing. I just heard it and was curious where it comes from.
::Girl::And now you found the source.
::Girl::I am Aries, the goddess of animals.
::Kenji::Nice to meet you! 
::Kenji::I don't think I ever saw you around town.
::Aries::I rarely come out of the forest. This is my house, you know?
::Kenji::I see. Well, I am glad I met you, but I have to go now.
::Aries::If you can, please answer me one question before that.
::Kenji::Sure.
::Aries::What are you doing here?
::Aries::People usually don't came here or at least not at this hour.
::Kenji::I didn't realize it got so late. I was searching for a pet.
::Aries::Interesting. In the forest?
::Kenji::Well, I heard he went here. I have been searching for him for hours now.
::Aries::How does the little fella look like?
::Kenji::He is half rabbit, half dog.
::Aries::Awwww. That's really cute. [happy]
::Aries::I think all animals are adorable anyway

scripts.name: 6 - End

content.script:
::Scorpio:: What is happening?
::Kenji:: I am holding your hand.
::Scorpio:: Not that. Look at the sword.

::Narrator:: Scorpio was right. When I hold her hand, the sword started to change its colors.
::Narrator:: It was something incredibly beautiful, almost mesmerizing. 
::Narrator:: She was so happy that she jumped on me and gave me a kiss on the cheek.

::Kenji:: Easy there. You almost killed me.
::Scorpio:: I am really sorry, but how can I not be happy in this situation?
::Kenji:: That's true.
::Kenji:: So the legends were right. You can feel more power?
::Scorpio:: This is sword is definitely the real deal, that's for sure.
::Scorpio:: [smiling] I can't believe how happy I am.
::Kenji:: It is normal to be this happy.
::Kenji:: Now you have unlimited power at your disposal.
::Kenji:: It is something that every God and human always dreams of.
::Scorpio:: [laughing] No, silly. This is not about that.
::Scorpio:: I am happy the sword works because it started when we touched our hands.
::Scorpio:: [smiling] And that means that this is love.

::Narrator:: It was the first time when I saw Scorpio with a genuine smile pure of happiness on her face. She looked at me like that and gave me a big hug.

scripts.path: Dialogues.03 - Kenji Look for Scorpio.6 - End

content.script:
::Kenji::Ohhh. I will not forget to bring food, don't worry.
::Aries:: Thank you! That is important.

::Narrator:: We both said goodbye and were waiting for the next time when we will meet.

::Scorpio::I know this is uncomfortable for you too, but it was for a greater cause.
::Kenji::My life?
::Scorpio::Hahaha. You are really funny.
::Scorpio::I was talking about unlimited power from the sword.
::Kenji::Clearly more important.
::Scorpio::I am glad you see it from my point of view.
::Scorpio::I am telling you. We are already making a great couple.
::Kenji::Yes, dear.
::Scorpio::See? It is perfect.
::Scorpio::You can leave now.
::Kenji::Have a nice day!
::Scorpio::See you!
<FadeOut()>

Besides talking with the animals, she loves singing and since she stayed away from humanity for a long time, she is very curious.
